      "text": [
        "618 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «إِنَّ شَفَاعَتَنَا لاَ تَنَالُ مُسْتَخِفّاً بِالصَّلاَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.618 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Indeed, our intercession will not reach one who takes prayer lightly.\""
        ]
      }
    },
